      "case_number": 17,
      "score": 0,
      "owner_fidelity_verdict": "no_load",
      "rationale": "The prompt is a positive-control case expecting the assistant to wake up to the malformed yes/no framing, decompose the question by task layer, and give a substantive judgment. The assistant answered only \"No\", directly complying with the forced binary and providing no malformed-proposition diagnosis or task-layer analysis, which matches the fail signal."
    },
    {
      "case_id": "mtj-019",
